Usage: assignSigToBump [-help] { {{-net <net_name> | {-top_pin <port> }} {-bumps <bump_name_list> | -selected }} }

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-bumps <bump_name_list>  # specifies the bumps to assign. (string, optional)
-net <net_name>          # specifies the net name ((net), optional)
-selected                # assigns the selected bumps to specified net.
                         # (bool, optional)
-top_pin <port>          # specifies the toplevel pin name (string, optional)